# Roadmap

## Phase 1

* Entity definitions
* Feature definitions
* Local registry

## Phase 2

* Offline feature store
* Historical feature retrieval
* Point-in-time joins
* Training dataset generation

## Phase 3

* SQLite online store
* Materialization
* Online inference API

## Phase 4

* CLI
* Better documentation
* Real-world examples
* Type hints
* Unit tests

## Phase 5

* Redis backend
* Feature transformations
* Feature validation
* Versioning
* PyPI release

